Quickstrike:



"Fine," he said with a growing frown. "Don't like this." He didn't 
like being used to lug around supplies like before this Neo Beast 
Wars. He was supposed to be a higher rank. Didn't the lower ranks do 
this sort of work? He knew that. He was once one of them.

He took a few steps forward. "What kinda slag they want us t' carry?"
